<header><section>
<p>Coming 2027</p>
</section></header><section>
<p>As part of the 30th anniversary Pokémon celebrations, Game Freak lifted the lid on its new mainline game <a href="https://www.nintendolife.com/games/nintendo-switch-2/pokemon-winds-and-waves">Pokémon Winds &amp; Waves</a>.</p>
<p>This game is coming exclusively to the Switch 2 in 2027 and includes a new open world to explore, as well as a "beautiful windswept islands and a vast ocean with glittering waves". There are also new Pokémon to meet, catch and train.</p>
<p>Here's a look at what you expect when these games arrive "exclusively" on the Switch 2:</p>
